Hello!
I've rebased my PR for constify-ing Duration methods https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/pull/72481 now that const_if_match is stable and I tried to request a review from @oli but rust-highfive did not pick it up
isn't oli already assigned to that pr?
Ah hu maybe? I don't know how to check that
But the labels should be set a waiting-for-review or something no?
it's on the right side column of the desktop view
I don't know if the review state labels can be automatically changed if you are not a member
Ah right thanks @Lokathor ! I thought it was some hidden bors status but its actually just a github assignee
And thanks @lcnr for fixing the labels. I really thought re-requesting a review would make bors (or rust-highfive?) to reset the labels
